// Dragnet [Container]: dragnet-container-2026-3188 — Vulnerable Base Image Pull
// Status: deprecated | Level: critical | ID: 322a2f40-700e-5caa-aa19-9c7000fa2e0d

any where
  (process.executable like~ "*oraclelinux:5*" or process.executable like~ "*oraclelinux:6*" or process.executable like~ "*ubuntu:12.04*")
